{"id":291014,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-上海维权人士尹慧敏医疗纠纷案三次要求/","date":"2013-04-28T21:15:48Z","modified":"2013-04-28T21:15:48Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士尹慧敏医疗纠纷案三次要求审判长回避无果","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点</span><span>，上海上访维权人士尹慧敏诉上海徐汇区中心医院（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>）徐民一（民）初字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">959</span><span>号医疗损害责任纠纷案，在徐汇区法院第十法庭公开审理。尹慧敏的部分朋友（按签名单上签名的前后排列）：刘福泉、刘桂芳、张洪祥、周荣清、陈建芳、毛恒凤、徐希芳、丁德元等人到庭参加旁听。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>尹慧敏的父亲（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月份）高血糖被被告（徐汇区中心医院）加输葡萄糖滴液后并发症死亡，母亲（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月份）因肺炎在治疗过程中未康复被被告（徐汇区中心医院）赶出医院，导致两肺炎重症死亡。尹慧敏认为上海市徐汇区中心医院在诊疗过程中有严重的医疗过错。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>理由之一</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>：涂改病史篡改病史；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>理由之二：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>严重缺失客观病史；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>理由之三：抢夺病人自管病史；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>理由之四：伪造篡改和添加病史和再销毁伪造的证据；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>理由之五：医生签名不一致。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>由于被告的责任，造成尹慧敏失去父母双亲。为了讨一个说法，尹慧敏诉讼至徐汇区法院，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日立案。因尹慧敏知道为自己审理（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>）年徐民一（民）初字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">959</span><span>号医疗损害责任纠纷案的审判长是高霄雷，此人审理过许多案子都是枉法裁判。尹慧敏于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>连续两次向上海市徐汇区法院书面提出申请要求审判长高霄雷回避，上海市徐汇区法院不予支持原告回避请求。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-fn75QBPBv1U/UX1Ngly6A3I/AAAAAAAAhEk/nuR6-wg3u9o/s1600/P1010693.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-fn75QBPBv1U/UX1Ngly6A3I/AAAAAAAAhEk/nuR6-wg3u9o/s320/P1010693.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-5AtXL2LSsOc/UX1NkA7G7tI/AAAAAAAAhEs/EG-e3Vrfa54/s1600/PTDC0082.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-5AtXL2LSsOc/UX1NkA7G7tI/AAAAAAAAhEs/EG-e3Vrfa54/s320/PTDC0082.JPG\" width=\"238\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}